For example, the fact that there are children entertaining adults who could be said to be from the 'elite'. One of the things that caught my attention was the way Justin is dressed, as I am not a fan, I thought he had dyed his hair pink and so because he had changed his style, but, after remembering Antonio LA Raid's words (I think he was his manager or something like that, I don't remember), saying that he (Justin) has "a woman's beauty" (or something similar), I understand why Justin wears a pearl necklace at first, and Then a bright one, with earrings and wearing all pink. There are many important points in the lyrics and the video, and it would be too long for me to explain, but I think you should consider taking a closer look at the whole topic and the correlation between Yummy and the Pizza Gate thing. I guess there should be several twitter threads and videos on YouTube explaining everything (at least in Spanish there are many).
Sorry if you don't understand or there are spelling mistakes.
